00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:19,960
I want my umbrella back.

573
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:23,400
Okay, okay.

574
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:25,490
I don't mean anything else.

575
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:27,840
I just think giving an umbrella as a gift is bad luck.

576
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:29,500
I'll give you something else.

577
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:30,920
Yuanbao.

578
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:39,400
We're already in a mutual help group, and you still get extra tutoring?

579
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,600
Why don't you tutor me too?

580
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:42,130
You don't need my tutoring.

581
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,200
Deskmate, I'll go first.

582
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:45,160
Goodbye.

583
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:47,060
Bye, see you tomorrow.

584
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:50,210
This kid actually knows some manners.

585
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:52,160
What was he talking to you about?

586
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,480
Nothing much, just saying hi.

587
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:07,800
What time is it?

588
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:10,040
Did they cancel their date?

589
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,400
I'm sure he's at home.

590
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:14,920
If their date is canceled today,

591
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:17,720
that proves our mission is accomplished.

592
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:20,520
When sisters unite, they are unstoppable.

593
00:31:21,560 --> 00:31:23,320
Do you remember

594
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,080
their expressions after you said that?

595
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:27,000
It was like a bolt from the blue.

596
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:29,570
They were completely dumbstruck on the spot.

597
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:31,760
There's no problem we can't solve.
